# TypeScript

The instructions below is only for the file which has a format of "*.test.ts"

- Use the vitest library to make unit test.
- Use the vitest library to mock function.

# TypeScript React

The instructions below is only for the file which has a format of "*.test.tsx"

- Use the vitest library to make unit test.
- Use the vitest library to mock function.
- Use the @testing-library/react to test react component rendering and interaction to a component.
- Use the @testing-library/user-event to simulate browser interactions.